---
By: Francis de Sales
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 195
    Verse: 10
Tags:
  - God's Will
---
We should ask nothing and refuse nothing, but leave ourselves in the arms
of divine Providence without wasting time in any desire, except to will
what God wills of us.
